{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So just standing, doing what other people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cleaning, do other things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- but it was taken away, the portion that I had doubled.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like if you don't want to do this kind, doing what they told you to, hitting, and then you're not gonna get more-- more eat-- food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sol-- I told you, I was separated from my brother in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was still working now in Ostrowiec in that factory, and I was sent to Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So by the time they liquidated Blizyn, they liquidated my hometown, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was sent-- he was in Auschwitz, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in Birkenau, but I didn't know about him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't know about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was sent to Buna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Buna is eight kilometers from Auschwitz, from Birkenau, and Buna was the big factories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans had all factories that would make ammunition called IG Farben.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the name of the Buna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what happened to me after a few months being in Birkeanu, they-- it was a Sunday, and they took us from Auschwitz Birkenau in appell.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was-- that-- taken out, too, and we put in-- in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we all naked, stripped naked completely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what we waiting-- we was waiting for somebody to come, SS, to check us out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the evening it was-- came a few SS, and they had Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Josef Mengele was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How'd I know it Mengele?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That voice or the pictures, and I remember exactly him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Never got out of my eyes when I saw him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what we had to do-- it was a long barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the middle of the barracks was that brick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You couldn't go across, you had to go around, all around to the edge.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
